WEBVTT

00:00:01.261 --> 00:00:02.753
Predstavljajte si,

00:00:02.753 --> 00:00:04.708
kakšen dosežek je bil to

00:00:04.708 --> 00:00:07.136
za ženske, ki so bile žrtve nasilja

00:00:07.136 --> 00:00:09.092
v 1980-ih.

00:00:09.092 --> 00:00:12.605
Prišle so na urgenco,

00:00:12.605 --> 00:00:16.017
zaradi, kot so temu rekli policisti,
"ljubezenskega prepirčka",

00:00:16.017 --> 00:00:19.792
jaz pa sem videla pretepeno žensko,

00:00:19.792 --> 00:00:24.534
videla sem zlomljen nos in zapestje

00:00:24.534 --> 00:00:26.295
in zatečene oči.

00:00:26.295 --> 00:00:30.333
Kot aktivisti
smo vzeli polaroidni fotoaparat,